snippet.title: No prince needed (by ArmedPandaGames) - free offline puzzle platform game for Android - gameplay.
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching and likes! 

No prince needed is an adorable 2D puzzle platformer where you play as a princess which was kidnapped by evil wizard. Use ability to throw boxes and solve unique puzzles. Escape the castle with the power of your intelligence and platforming skills!

Featuring:
- 45 levels to beat.
- Variety of traps.
- Collectable coins.
- 4 character skins.
- Pixel art graphics.
- No ads.


Free offline game.

Google Play download URL:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ArmedPandaGames.Noprinceneeded

List of Platformers on the channel:
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLN49z9Rp4EXwX0QA_ggfIRYDqk8lxTOs4
